playstore_details.title: Shopee TH: Online shopping app
playstore_details.description:
Shopee, a platform for shopping online, buying and selling things online, is prevalent in Southeast Asia and Taiwan.
Shopee has a wide range of products, easy to use, high security with standardized payment and logistics systems.

online shopping anywhere, anytime at Shopee with many services and special promotions.

● Shopee is now available in three languages – Thai, English, and Burmese – to ensure a smoother and more personalized shopping experience for everyone! Enjoy seamless navigation, localized content, and easier access to your favorite deals—no matter what language you speak.
● Shopping, buy and sell online with products from many categories. Many stores such as health and beauty electrical appliance electronics fashion clothes Home appliances, amulets, toys, mother and child products, and much more.
● Fast delivery in Bangkok and surrounding areas, approximately 1-2 business days*, provincial or distant areas approximately 2-5 business days*.
● Buy discounted products, Flash Sale, updated every day and recommended products selected for you.
● Shopee Mall: top brand products Genuine brand, sure cheap Whether it's beauty or fashion products, you can shop online with peace of mind.
● Shopee is definitely cheap. Shopee product zone has been selected as being the cheapest. If you find a cheaper store elsewhere, you'll get your money back 100%*.
● Shopee Rewards allows Shopee Memberships members to shop online and accumulate balance. Collect free shipping codes every month.
● Shopee Prizes have the most fun with games that are ready to give away codes and Coins every day for you to continue shopping for good value.
● Shopee LIVE: Watch fun live streams in real time. Live, ask and answer everything, see products, clothes, accessories from every angle.
● Shopee Video: Watch product reviews as short video content. The clips are both fun and informative, plus they're easy to shop and sell quickly.
● Shopee Affiliate Programs allow merchants or users to just share and earn money from every order that people place through affiliate links.
● Shopee Food allows you to order food online. Delivered directly to your home from popular stores. With many discounts.
● SPayLater - Pay in flexible installments from 1 to 24 months. Effective Interest Rate cap at 25%* For example, if you purchase an item worth ฿1,000 and choose to pay in 3 months with SPayLater, you will have a monthly repayment amount of ฿341.7. Total ฿1,025.1 consists of ฿1,000 principal and ฿25.1 interest (at Effective Interest Rate 15% p.a.).
● SEasyCash - Pay in flexible installments from 2 to 36 months. Effective Interest Rate cap at 33%* For example, if you withdraw ฿1,000 and choose to pay in 3 months, you will have a monthly repayment amount of ฿347 in the first two months and ฿350 in the last month. Total ฿1,045 consists of ฿1,000 principal and ฿45 interest (at Effective Interest Rate 25% p.a.).
*Now available for invitation only and no document required.*

-------------------

Follow news and good deals from us via the following channels.
Visit our website at www.shopee.co.th
Like our Facebook at facebook.com/ShopeeTH
Follow and update new trends from us on Instagram @shopee_TH
Follow our news and promotions on Line at @ShopeeTH
Office location: Rasa Two, 1818 Petchaburi Rd, Kwaeng Makkasan, Khet Ratchathewi, Bangkok 10400

* Conditions are as specified by the company.

*According to App Annie's (or Data.ai) report, in the first quarter of 2020, 'Shopee' was ranked as the number 1 shopping application in the number of monthly active users (Monthly Active Users), the highest in Southeast Asia and Taiwan.

**'Shopee' is the number one e-commerce platform that is pleasing to both buyers and sellers. From the results of a survey of internet user behavior in Thailand in 2019 by the Electronic Transactions Development Agency (ETDA).

warning.title: Application Data can be Backed up
warning.description:
[android:allowBackup] flag is missing.
The flag [android:allowBackup] should be set to false. By default it is set to true and allows anyone to backup your application data via adb. It allows users who have enabled USB debugging to copy application data off of the device.

hotspot.title: Found 3 critical permission(s)
hotspot.description:
Ensure that these permissions are required by the application.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE (dangerous): read/modify/delete external storage contents - Allows an application to write to external storage.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE (dangerous): read phone state and identity - Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE (dangerous): read external storage contents - Allows an application to read from external storage.
